				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-C%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/B%E1%BB%87nh-ng%C6%B0u/poem-05BoFPmU8C4wySIgiCGEOA">Bệnh ngưu - 病牛</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-C%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-__w9A4eZId-5itdRrNhRCA">Lý Cương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%AD-Ngang/C%E1%BA%A3m-ng%E1%BB%99-k%E1%BB%B3-29/poem-Neua5H6zZsk4k31QZ-oStQ">Cảm ngộ kỳ 29 - 感遇其二十九</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%AD-Ngang/author-KAeplXpuQBYC4UQBLqb_RQ">Trần Tử Ngang</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%ADu-C%E1%BB%A7ng/%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-l%C3%A2n-t%E1%BA%A9u/poem-RKgI_E38rmdnpIhvi0UJHg">Đại lân tẩu - 代鄰叟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%ADu-C%E1%BB%A7ng/author-qI9UHMMflLE3z07EmEsamw">Đậu Củng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng-Nguy%C3%AAn-s%E1%BB%A9-qu%C3%A2n-Thung-L%C4%83ng-h%C3%A0nh/poem-0MPVf1G_1Kh6ZzHTaLZzyA">Đồng Nguyên sứ quân “Thung Lăng hành” - 同元使君舂陵行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/H%E1%BB%89-v%C4%83n-quan-qu%C3%A2n-d%C4%A9-l%C3%A2m-t%E1%BA%B7c-c%E1%BA%A3nh-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem--7aSmm5Sn3I7FvPVGG4inQ">Hỉ văn quan quân dĩ lâm tặc cảnh, nhị thập vận - 喜聞官軍已臨賊境二十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Luy-tu%E1%BA%A5n/poem-JUG7aeitCSfKlc_AMUPlQQ">Luy tuấn - 羸駿</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nhan-Nh%C3%A2n-%C3%9Ac/N%C3%B4ng-gia/poem-pLF2a0ExCKd9WVDTT0zuDA">Nông gia - 農家</a>